{"tid":2410820,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BLACKPINK ROSÉ過生日「粉絲朝貢」引爭議！真的太寒心了VS粉絲送的禮物可以收","createTime":"2021-02-17T02:24:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T07:39:06.000Z","uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"39eaa5c9c70953b93109454ed5bf7dff18330f40","tid":2410820,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T02:24:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_673385675ac2f0d4607be52870abbb92/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-16/133703-897063.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_673385675ac2f0d4607be52870abbb92%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-16%2F133703-897063.png&h=f657b6ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n粉絲朝貢是飯圈特有的文化，粉絲們除了送本命飽含真心的親筆信之外，還會賺錢為他們買高價名牌禮物。<br />\n<br />\n2月11日是BLACKPINK成員 ROS&Eacute;的生日，那一天她就收到了很多禮物，從粉絲們公開的禮物清單來看，有價值數百萬的名牌包、皮鞋、寶石和衣服等等，數量多達有數十個，總價也在上億元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/blackpink.closet.indo/?utm_source=ig_embed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fblackpink.closet.indo%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BexpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=6422438a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/blackpink.closet.indo/?utm_source=ig_embed</a><br />\n<br />\n得知這件事情的很多網民們在網路上留言表示羡慕，稱：「一整年都不需要購物了」、「明星的人生」、「羡慕死了」等。 但也有部份網民對此持不同意見，表示：「這是幹什麼，太讓人寒心了」、「粉絲不送她也有錢買，作為粉絲就該給她買禮物？ 」、「這就是歌手有問題啊，一開始就應該明說不收粉絲禮物，這樣粉絲也不會攢錢，壓力還小一些，又不是財閥，財閥該送鑽石才對，這可是粉絲們攢了一年的錢。 」對於這些不同的聲音，也有網民幫助ROSE反駁，稱：「粉絲有能力送這些，你們有什麼好寒心的」、「這些都是粉絲自己攢的錢，偶爾還會有很有錢的粉絲投資」、「你們就是羡慕嫉妒恨，有什麼好酸的。 」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/roses_are_rosie/?utm_source=ig_embed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Froses_are_rosie%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BexpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=0de8fdb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/roses_are_rosie/?utm_source=ig_embed</a><br />\n<br />\n粉絲朝貢一直存在著較大的爭議，作為粉絲認為本命一年一次的生日，大家希望給對方一份難忘的禮物，而購買禮物的金額也是廣大粉絲均攤。 相反，也有很多人認為朝貢文化根本就是「慣壞了」明星，更重要的是這種「朝貢」會在飯圈形成攀比之風，導致粉絲團的壓力越來越大。<br />\n<br />\n「圖：IG@blackpink.closet.indo、@roses_are_rosie」"},{"pid":"a618fdb6ff32d8a0329b6adec851e30e97d31b00","tid":2410820,"uid":93096,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T02:25:19.000Z","msg":"想收禮物...<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4188951efd48ab2453e020f217471a66b6ea57d9","tid":2410820,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a618fdb6ff32d8a0329b6adec851e30e97d31b00","tid":2410820,"uid":93096,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T02:25:19.000Z","msg":"想收禮物...<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T02:26:42.000Z","msg":"太大貪了<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53e3ef3e2b3b8faef33b741b41ba44b1d21f8a8e","tid":2410820,"uid":55519,"like":88,"dislike":1,"score":87,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T02:31:02.000Z","msg":"其實有好多粉絲係死慳死抵儲黎買既 不過人地追星仆心仆命 冇計啦"},{"pid":"34be7b92df69fa1abcf5953d2d19c83af6555e60","tid":2410820,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"53e3ef3e2b3b8faef33b741b41ba44b1d21f8a8e","tid":2410820,"uid":55519,"like":88,"dislike":1,"score":87,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T02:31:02.000Z","msg":"其實有好多粉絲係死慳死抵儲黎買既 不過人地追星仆心仆命 冇計啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T02:31:49.000Z","msg":"好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e58029137ac335fbe2a896393d3049578af9db78","tid":2410820,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4188951efd48ab2453e020f217471a66b6ea57d9","tid":2410820,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a618fdb6ff32d8a0329b6adec851e30e97d31b00","tid":2410820,"uid":93096,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T02:25:19.000Z","msg":"想收禮物...<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},